<%- include('./partials/header') %>

<main class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-24" style="background-color: #FAFAFA;">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 max-w-4xl">
        <!-- Hero Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 brand-font" style="color: #1E1E1E;">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold text-sm">Last Updated: March 2024</p>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 mx-auto mt-8" style="background-color: #B76E79;"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-12">
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 brand-font flex items-center gap-3" style="color: #1E1E1E;">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm" style="background-color: #B76E79;">1</span>
                    Introduction
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    At URBAN ÉLITE, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our distinguished clientele. This policy outlines how we handle your personal data with the same care and precision we apply to our curated collections. By using our services, you entrust us with your information, and we take that responsibility with the utmost seriousness.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 brand-font flex items-center gap-3" style="color: #1E1E1E;">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm" style="background-color: #B76E79;">2</span>
                    Information We Collect
                </h2>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-xl mt-1" style="color: #B76E79;"></i>
                            <span><strong>Personal Identity:</strong> Name, email address, and phone number for account management.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-xl mt-1" style="color: #B76E79;"></i>
                            <span><strong>Lifestyle Preferences:</strong> Style choices and browsing behavior used to curate your personal experience.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-xl mt-1" style="color: #B76E79;"></i>
                            <span><strong>Logistics Data:</strong> Shipping addresses and delivery instructions for our concierge service.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 brand-font flex items-center gap-3" style="color: #1E1E1E;">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm" style="background-color: #B76E79;">3</span>
                    The Secure Vault Protocol
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Your financial and sensitive data is handled via our proprietary "Secure Vault" protocol. We use bank-grade 256-bit encryption and never store full credit card details on our primary servers.
                </p>
                <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 italic border-l-4" style="border-color: #B76E79;">
                    "Our security measures are designed to ensure that your private life remains precisely that—private."
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 brand-font flex items-center gap-3" style="color: #1E1E1E;">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm" style="background-color: #B76E79;">4</span>
                    How We Use Your Data
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    We use your information exclusively to provide a seamless luxury experience. This includes personalizing your dashboard, facilitating white-glove delivery, and providing priority support from our elite concierge team. We never sell your data to third parties.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 brand-font flex items-center gap-3" style="color: #1E1E1E;">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm" style="background-color: #B76E79;">5</span>
                    Your Global Rights
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Regardless of your location, you have the right to access, rectify, or request the deletion of your personal data at any time. Our concierge team is ready to assist you with any privacy-related inquiries.
                </p>
            </section>

        </article>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-20 p-12 rounded-3xl text-center shadow-xl" style="background-color: #1E1E1E; color: white;">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 brand-font">Questions About Your Privacy?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto">Our dedicated concierge team is available to discuss any concerns you may have regarding your data.</p>
            <a href="/#contact" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1" style="background-color: #B76E79; color: white;">
                Contact Concierge
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
